original: Löfgren, Nils Magnus, tandläkare, Borås, f. 17/4/12 i Eksjö av Carl L. o. Hilma Bergander. G. 40 m. Hilde->gard Ahnborg. Barn: Monica f. 43. — Tandhex. 39. Praktik i Borås sed. 39, militärtandl. v. Älvsb. reg. sed. 43.
translated: Löfgren, Nils Magnus, dentist, Borås, born on April 17, 1912 in Eksjö to Carl L. and Hilma Bergander. Married in 1940 to Hildegarde Ahnborg. Children: Monica, born in 1943. Dental assistant in 1939. Practiced in Borås since 1939, military dentist for the Älvsborg regiment since 1943.
